cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.MM

The paper deals with implementing convolutional neural networks for keyword spotting in the browser, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
